milestones.description: Wasim Raja has broken the record for most sixes (4) in ODIs for PAK, going past Javed Miandad's 3
Graham Roope and David Gower's 105-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 83 between John Edrich and Fletcher
Wasim Bari has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for PAK, going past Wasim Raja
